00:01:00.449 --> 00:01:06.620
Boosting brains to learn a thousand times
faster would happen sometime down the road.

00:01:06.620 --> 00:01:12.610
A new hybrid power fabric uses solar as well
as mechanical movement to harness power.

00:01:12.610 --> 00:01:17.620
Solar cells are made into micro-cable structures
and woven with nanogenerators to create the

00:01:17.620 --> 00:01:19.150
smart fabric.

00:01:19.150 --> 00:01:23.470
Not only does it charge using ambient light
but the mechanical movement allows wind and

00:01:23.470 --> 00:01:26.030
human motion to gather energy.

00:01:26.030 --> 00:01:30.060
And researchers from the Georgie Institute
of Technology say the fabric could be used

00:01:30.060 --> 00:01:34.590
