augmented driving device that allows GPS navigation

00:01:43.700 --> 00:01:47.150
and phone access without taking your eyes
off the road.

00:01:47.150 --> 00:01:52.281
The steering wheel dial allows for scrolling
through or skipping songs and zooming in and

00:01:52.281 --> 00:01:57.610
out of the map while gesture controls handle
accepting and dismissing phone calls.

