they just started shipping this week.

00:02:02.890 --> 00:02:06.880
A brain implant allows you to feel with a
robotic hand.

00:02:06.880 --> 00:02:11.209
Neuroengineers at the University Of Pittsburg
used magnetic resonance imaging to map the

00:02:11.209 --> 00:02:15.829
regions of the patient’s brain associated
with imagining a touch on different parts

00:02:15.829 --> 00:02:16.829
